---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <main>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      If you contact us by e-mail, the data provided will be stored by us in
      order to process your request. As a data subject, you have the right to
      information, the right to rectification or deletion, the right to restrict
      processing and the right to object to the processing of your data. If you
      have given us consent, you can revoke this at any time with effect for the
      future. Please send your objection [or revocation] informally to the
      following address: <a href="mailto:mail@henrygressmann.de"
        >mail@henrygressmann.de</a
      >. If you have given us consent, you can revoke it at any time with effect
      for the future.
    </p>

    <h3>What information do we collect?</h3>
    <p>
      Just your email address and name. Outside of that, only the files you
      upload are stored on our servers. We don't store any other information
      about you. IP addresses are always transmitted when you visit a website,
      but we only store a hashed version of it.
    </p>

    <h3>How do we use your information?</h3>
    <p>
      We only use your email address to personally contact you. We don't share
      your email address with anyone else. Files you upload are publicly visible
      to anyone with the link. Even when storing files outside of the public
      folder, we don't guarantee that they are private.
    </p>

    <h3>Who processes your information?</h3>
    <p>
      Our server runs on a Server hosted by Hetzner Online GmbH. Communication
      with our server is alway encrypted. We don't log any information about
      you, expect what is required to secure the login process.
    </p>

    <h3>How can I delete my information?</h3>
    <p>
      You can delete your account at any time. This will delete all files you
      uploaded. If you want to delete your account, please <a href="/imprint"
        >contact us</a
      >.
    </p>

    <style>
      h1 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      h3 {
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0.2rem;
      }

      main {
        padding: 1rem;
        height: fit-content;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        flex: 1;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 40rem;
      }
    </style>
  </main>
</Layout>
